n terms of future presidents.=E2=80=9D And on <i>Face the Nation</i>, Minne=
sota Democratic Sen. <b>Amy Klobuchar </b>said =E2=80=9Cthis whole process =
cries out for reform because otherwise you undermine the justice system. =
=E2=80=A6 Let=E2=80=99s at least look at these on a factual basis and a ris=
k basis, instead of just in the middle of the night a month before a presid=
